data.description: Get away from the congestion and plant roots outside city limits! This open concept two story has a secondary bedroom with a full bath on the first floor, perfect for an office or for any family member to enjoy! Wind down your day by enjoying the vast views from your backyard or get active in the community pool and playground down the street! This beautiful home is located 15 minutes from Lackland AFB and has immediate access to Loop 1604 and Hwy 90! The home loan is assumable, so you can take over the same mortgage payment with a 3.25% rate! Call to schedule your private home tour today!
